"536","<p style=margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;margin-right:22.3pt;margin-top:0in;><font color=black face=Times New Roman lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;line-height:13.8pt;>Dreyfus/Laurel Funds Trust:</font></p>"
"537","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;><font color=black face=Times New Roman lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>Page 2</font></p>"
"538","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;><font color=black face=Times New Roman lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>&nbsp;</font></p>"
"539","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;><font color=black face=Times New Roman lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>A deficiency in internal control"
"540","over financial reporting exists when the design or operation of a control does"
"541","not allow management or employees, in the normal course of performing their"
"542","assigned functions, to prevent or detect misstatements on a timely basis.</font></p>"
"543","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;><font color=black face=Times New Roman lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;>A material weakness is a"
"544","deficiency, or a combination of deficiencies, in internal control over"
"545","financial reporting, such that there is a reasonable possibility that a"
"546","material misstatement of the Funds&#8217; annual or interim financial statements will not be"
"547","prevented or detected on a timely basis.</font></p>"
"548","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;><font color=black face=Times New Roman lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;line-height:13.8pt;>&#160; &nbsp;</font></p>"
"549","<p style=margin-bottom:13.9pt;margin-left:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-top:0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;><font color=black face=Times New Roman lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;line-height:13.8pt;>Our consideration of the Funds&#8217; internal control over"
"550","financial reporting was for the limited purpose described in the first"
"551","paragraph and would not necessarily disclose all deficiencies in internal"
"552","control that might be material weaknesses under standards established by the"
"553","Public Company Accounting Oversight Board (United States).&#160; However, we noted"
"554","no deficiencies in the Funds&#8217; internal control over financial reporting and its"
"555","operation, including controls over safeguarding securities that we consider to"
"556","be a material weakness as defined above as of May 31, 2013.<sup><font color=black style=position:relative;top:-5.5pt;></font></sup></font><sup><font color=black style=position:relative;top:-5.5pt;><font color=black face=Times New Roman lang=EN-US style=font-size:8.0pt;line-height:13.8pt;> </font></font></sup></p>"
"557","<p style=margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;><font color=black face=Times New Roman lang=EN-US style=font-size:12.0pt;line-height:13.8pt;>This report is intended solely for the information and use"
"558","of management and the Board of Trustees and shareholders of Dreyfus/Laurel"
"559","Funds Trust and the Securities and Exchange Commission and is not intended to"
